== Role Overview

=== Position Details
- *Role Title*: Credit Analyst
- *Hierarchy Level*: Junior to Mid-level (typically 1-4 years post-university)
- *Division*: Investment Team
- *Institution Type*: Fixed Income / Credit Fund Manager
- *Example Firms*: Janus Henderson Investors, PIMCO Australia, Bentham Asset Management, Metrics Credit Partners

=== Position in Organisation
Credit Analysts sit within the Investment Team, reporting to Senior Credit Analysts, Portfolio Managers, or Heads of Credit. They work closely with:
- Portfolio Managers (Investment Grade, High Yield, Distressed)
- Trading desks
- Risk Management teams
- Quantitative Analysts

